sequenceDiagram
    box Frontend
        participant B as Browser
    end
    box Backend
        participant S as Server
        participant D as Database
    end
    B->>+S: GET /page
    S->>+D: query rows
    D-->>-S: result set
    S-->>-B: 200 OK
    Note over B: render DOM
    B->>+S: POST /job
    create participant W as Worker
    S->>+W: enqueue task
    W-->>-S: ack
    S-->>-B: 202 Accepted
    loop every 30s
        B->>S: poll updates
        S-->>B: 204 No Content
    end
    destroy W
    S-xW: shutdown
